PrecisAppointment of a TEMPORARY ADMINISTRATOR, namely Mr. Justice THOMAS C. WAKELING, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Saskatchewan, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of SASKATCHEWAN over the course of a five-day period in September, 1992 (21st to the 25th).
